<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.3">
<l>tītaṟu tiṅkaḷ poṅku cuṭarumpa rumpa rulakēḻi ṉōṭu muṭaṉē</l>
<l>mātira maṇcu mantu vaṭakuṉṟu niṉṟa malaiyāṟu mēḻu kaṭalum</l>
<l>pātamar cūḻku ḷampi ṉakamaṇṭa latti ṉorupālō ṭuṅka vaḷarcēr</l>
<l>ātimu ṉēṉa māki yaraṇāya mūrtti yatunammai yāḷu maracē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sovereign who rules us is the god who became a refuge as a boar</l>
<l rend="indent">long ago at the beginning,</l>
<l>Who swelled [and] grew so that the faultless moon, blazing sun,</l>
<l rend="indent">the celestials, the celestials’ seven heavens all together,</l>
<l>The northern mountain bearing the earth, and the [four] quarters,</l>
<l rend="indent">the remaining six mountains, and the seven seas</l>
<l>Were tucked to one side of the curve in his round hoof</l>
<l rend="indent">on which his foot rests.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
